Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Self-proclaimed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...artificial human made by aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Self-proclaimed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...time traveling girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:10.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Self-proclaimed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...squad of esper boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:13.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Each one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:17.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...has shown me honest proof of their identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:18.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently, the three of them, each for their own reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:19.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kyon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...have been focusing on Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:22.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:23.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:25.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I accept everything that's happened or been said...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:27.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there is still one thing I just don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:31.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aliens, time travelers...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:33.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and the esper boys are swarming around Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:34.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...because, according to Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she wished for it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:39.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...been dragged into this bizarre mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:45.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a 100% genuine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:48.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...ordinary high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No special powers or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:53.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who came up with this scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:56.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it you, Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:00.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no concern of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:03.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why should I have to worry about this crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:05.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like everything is Haruhi's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:09.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she should be the one who has to worry about this, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:12.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as for Nagato, Koizumi, and Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:14.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...they should just tell everything directly to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:16.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever happens to the world afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:18.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...will be Haruhi's responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:19.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and have nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:21.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run around all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:22.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just don't get me involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:23.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:26.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Taniguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:29.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a normal high school student, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:32.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A normal high school student...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:36.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't push down a girl in an empty classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:40.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was Yuki Nagato, an A- by my ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:42.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The story going through Taniguchi's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:47.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is delusion, fantasy, and completely fictional.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagato was the unfortunate victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:52.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...when the literary club clubroom was turned into Haruhi's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was troubled...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:55.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so she came to me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had to sympathize with her sincere request...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so I felt I should help out the poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We decided to discuss remedial measures in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...after Haruhi had gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then Nagato's chronic anemia kicked in and she fainted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:12.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so I quickly put myself between her and the floor, which was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:15.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you happened to barge in, Taniguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:19.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed, once the truth has been brought to light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it seems like such a trivial thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:23.28,HaruhiManga,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(283,237)}Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.32,HaruhiManga,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs34\pos(510,222)}Bah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I believe your lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:31.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the fact that the antisocial Yuki Nagato would come to you for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:33.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...already makes you not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato was that famous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:38.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you're one of Suzumiya's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can be considered a normal high school student...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'm as normal as a water flea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Taniguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you use ESP?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally been infected by Suzumiya's poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:11.10,HaruhiTitleOverlay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs28\fad(490,460)\pos(96,50)}The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya VI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you getting changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:16.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to change again once I get to the clubroom anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have cleaning duty later, and it's easier to move in these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we have Mikuru-chan wear next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After bunny and maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the next would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:27.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitty ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nurse outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps a queen?
