Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:34.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nurse outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or a queâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who brought up the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so boring...
