Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just figure something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:08.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:09.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jacked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my name on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:16.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:17.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me, show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, this is just, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:27.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:30.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:31.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:33.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So maids turn you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:43.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:47.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm going to get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She never has any qualms about changing in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My arms and shoulders feel cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this outfit doesn't allow much ventilation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was today a costume party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't complicate the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:27.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They almost look like a pair of close sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably just wants to turn her into a maid with braids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it was what you would call an ordinary day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We didn't know what we wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We didn't know what we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We just let the clock tick by...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A moratorium sort of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The everyday happenings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...of a natural world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I did feel a bit dissatisfied...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...when nothing was going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:56.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could just tell myself, "Oh well. There's still plenty of time."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And aimlessly look to the next day and repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...this had its own sort of essence of the unordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and really wasn't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for almost getting killed by a classmate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and encountering some rampaging monster in a gray, uninhabited world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:11.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...those things just don't happen that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:16.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted everything to stay this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:17.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wouldn't anyone agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...normally?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there was someone who didn't agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:22.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I need them for art tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say something first next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Premeditated crime, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Incidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...do you know why people dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:07:00.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...rotates between cycles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...of REM and non-REM stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the body is resting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:06.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and the brain semi-active you're in REM sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is when we dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My alarm clock hasn't gone off yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wake your ass up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had woken up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but then I found myself in this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you were lying down next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:45.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was sleeping in my bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so how did I end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And the sky looks strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:07:59.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:00.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's escape from the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We might run into someone somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Especially at the fact that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It extends all the way around the school premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can't get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:39.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might as well just cling to my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Creates more of an atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:43.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:00.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Want tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:33.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is it just you and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go explore a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess that's typical of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting you to appear in a more tangible form...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell you a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an abnormal situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's normal closed space...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I am easily able to gain entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:13.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:16.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I could only appear in this incomplete form this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it was only after borrowing the power of all of my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it probably won't last very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The powers that rest within us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...are beginning to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Haruhi and I the only ones here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:33.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What we feared has already begun to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...has finally given up on the current world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:40.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and decided to create a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're on the brink of Armageddon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:46.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The higher-ups in our organization are in a state of panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows what will happen to our world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...once it has lost its God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:59.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If Suzumiya-san is feeling merciful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:02.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...our world may continue to exist without change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it could also return to nothing in the next second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:10.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you and Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...have completely vanished from our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not in ordinary closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an entirely new dimension created by Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps all the previous instances of closed space...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:25.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...were merely practice runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The world you are in is probably the manifestation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...nearest to the world Suzumiya-san desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we aren't sure what it is that she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, who knows what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have been chosen by Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The only person from the old world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Suzumiya-san truly wanted to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you had realized this long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that I'm almost out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The way things look now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I probably won't be seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to live in this gray world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...all alone with Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Adam and Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you reproduce enough it'll work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smack you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:13.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I would assume...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:16.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you should soon see a familiar-looking world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:17.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it probably won't be entirely the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:21.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I happen to be born into the new world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...please look after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer go back to the old world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If Suzumiya-san desires it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:29.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...then perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility is slim though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:36.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I would have liked to spend more time with you and Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I regret this turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to deliver messages from Mikuru Asahina and Yuki Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru Asahina wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry. It's all my fault."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:54.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Nagato said to turn on the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:56.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be going.
