Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you telling me to do, Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:52.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a mirage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:02.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the revival of some super weapon developed by an ancient race!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:12.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it'll attack us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:18.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's anything evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:28.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This weird world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that giant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:34.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to go back to our old world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stay in this place for the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like there's a place to eat when we get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I get the feeling it'll work itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having fun right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the SOS Brigade?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the club you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just gonna ditch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having this really fun experience right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:05.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to go look for anything mysterious anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out something after being thrown into this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I may complain all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I actually liked how my life was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Including that idiot Taniguchi and Kunikida...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi, Nagato, and Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:26.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...include the vanished Asakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:27.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I still have so many things I have to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:40.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This world won't be covered in darkness forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun will rise tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the old them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the old world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you fed up with that boring world!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:12.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want something more interesting to happen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I did indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:28.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been through some really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...interesting experiences the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:32.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you could say that the world is revolving around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You just didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the world was definitely moving in an interesting direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:48.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagato said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:50.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The potential for evolution."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to Asahina-san she was a "time warp."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koizumi treated her as "God. "
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does the person Haruhi Suzumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...mean to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:04.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi is Haruhi and nobody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not gonna use such tautology to dodge the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:06.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I don't happen to have a decisive answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:10.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:13.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If someone points to the classmate sitting behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and asks, "What is she to you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How are you supposed to respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess that's still dodging the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi isn't just a classmate to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, she isn't the potential for evolution...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or a time warp...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...much less God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Couldn't possibly be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what Snow White is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ponytails turn me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That ponytail you had back whenever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...looked so good it was criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The hell was that dream!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Freud would have a field day with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:29.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The most realistic dream l've ever had....?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:32.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:35.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is no longer the old world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the new world Haruhi created?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is there a way for me to confirm that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a nightmare last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up not getting any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never wanted to skip school as badly as I do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:05.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:13.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I won't be out of a job just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:45.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't discount the possibility that this world was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:46.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...newly created last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel privileged to meet you and Suzumiya-san again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:52.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Haruhi Suzumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:59.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...disappeared from this world for two and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:01.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How many others like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...are on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:04.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Many.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:09.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Will another one like Asakura attack me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:14.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:25.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I could see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd never...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...be able to return to this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:28.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:31.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We... We mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:33.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If Suzumiya-san sees us like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll happen all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a star-shaped mole around this spot on your chest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:51.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:55.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew it was shaped like a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:58.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-When did you see it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:22:00.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:05.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably sick of the maid outfit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:05.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:06.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:09.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop struggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Resistance is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:12.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you'll be a nurse. A nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:12.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:14.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do they say hospital attendant these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:15.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It means the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:19.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's talk a little about what happened afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:21.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally turned in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:24.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the paperwork for chartering the SOS Brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:26.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...into the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:28.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The save the world by overloading it with fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:30.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}....Haruhi Suzumiya's Brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:32.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...would definitely be rejected...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:34.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so I arbitrarily changed the name to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:37.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the support the student body by overworking to make the world a better place Student Service Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:41.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The city-wide "magical mystery patrol" is also going strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:43.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today would be the second occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:45.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By some freak coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:48.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Asahina-san, Nagato, and Koizumi were all suddenly unable to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:51.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I'm waiting for Haruhi myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I arrived an hour before the meeting time.
