Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:10.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have plenty of time to ask later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:12.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While Haruhi treats me at the cafÃ©.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:14.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact...
