Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:20.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like what kind of activities she has planned for the SOS Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:24.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The costumes I'd like to see Asahina-san in, etcetera etcetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:27.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But well, when it comes down to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already know what I'm going to tell her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:31.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, for now...
